column2: SELECT  G.objID,mn.ldist_z,G.u,G.g,G.r,G.i,G.z,a.h_alpha_flux,oii_flux, emline.sigmaStars as emline_vdisp, pca.vdisp_median as pca_vdisp, sp.veldisp as sp_vdisp FROM Galaxy as G join GalSpecLine as a on G.SpecobjID = a.SpecObjID left join stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON G.specobjid = pca.specobjid left join emissionLinesPort as emline on pca.specobjid = emline.specobjid left JOIN specObj as sp ON emline.specobjid = sp.specobjid left JOIN mangaDAPall as mn on G.htmID = mn.htmID
